Use the Repeater with separator when the user may need to repeat a set of  components or fields, e.g. for multiple sets of credit card or account details.

```jsx
<Repeater separator>
<FormGroup>
          <FormLabel htmlFor="formInput">Lable</FormLabel>
          <Input aria-describedby="formHint" className="w-full" id="formInput" name="test" />
        </FormGroup>
</Repeater>
```
